headline: Canopy Growth Corporation (CGC) Reports Q1 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: Canopy Growth (CGC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +6.67% and +8.81%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Tandem, Insulet monitoring CMS payment proposal for diabetes tech
summary: The proposal would introduce competitive bidding for insulin pumps and change how Medicare pays for diabetes devices, if finalized.
